name: Regression - CompTix BoC
description: The Test Suite contains regression steps for the CompTix BoC application used by Commissioners Office and MLB employees to request tickets.  Steps will vary by user-type (MLB / BOC) and user-privilege (User/Admin/Super Admin).

name: Regression - CompTix Team Site
description: The Test Suite contains regression steps for the CompTix Team application used by Teams to request tickets either non-digitally or through digital fulfillment (middleware). The application will function differently based on whether the user is assigned to a Team or a Crew (ex. Umpires), particularly in regards to setting up and making reservations.

name: Ticketing Admin - Basic Acceptance - For Automation
